n\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">compress</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> minLen<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token operator\">%</span> endraw <span class=\"token operator\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}